{"tid":447823,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣憎自己太廢？","createTime":"2017-10-25T16:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T19:34:37.000Z","uid":135967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de983a21fa36c1460050e00aa30c06d4b40145c5","tid":447823,"uid":135967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"屋企冇錢冇父幹<br />\n自己冇學歷冇擅長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又瘦又毒得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同一個好好既女仔一齊<br />\n佢又住私樓 屋企又有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有學歷有品味<br />\n<br />\n好想為佢而努力 比最好既佢<br />\n照顧佢 養佢<br />\n但好似點努力 都追唔上目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓價 通脹 人工低<br />\n<br />\n對唔住我真係好撚廢<br />\n呢條路我真係行唔到落去<br />\n我望唔到未來"},{"pid":"bcb398cc206945a80cc43aef8108eccb00c6ec26","tid":447823,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"食軟飯啦"},{"pid":"0c57c907dd0fe9b03046883d81df288db2fb74a9","tid":447823,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e8a3f06ba682432b00e28078704cbc5e4627dd","tid":447823,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"🍇"},{"pid":"f353a9174dc6ac4687259245017bc0b9639289c9","tid":447823,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"廢到永遠無疾而終<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b834f9deac91fec4fee4e28bd71d38e74adf82","tid":447823,"uid":13910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"廢到自己都唔想照鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e835dfc7ac4657d0f1aa80e2ade149af00de2","tid":447823,"uid":140222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"我都好憎<br />\n不過又會諗，如果真係咁想為左一個人而努力，應該堅持落去<br />\n埋怨自己廢都冇用，呢世人一定會遇到好多令自己成長同增值既事<br />\n為人地又好，為自己又好，唔好因為呢啲一時既感覺，令自己遲啲又再多一個遺憾<br />\n認真，我都唔係一個好正面既人，唔好屌我正面撚，只係理性啲咁諗，其實心態真係好緊要，會改變好多野"}]}